    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/3910da92501686639c35fc86e6a102a7.webp?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/080260566b2841162e7c6dc5d424a77e.poster.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/080260566b2841162e7c6dc5d424a77e.webm?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/080260566b2841162e7c6dc5d424a77e.mp4?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>满月的宅邸</strong>是一款全动画浪漫幻想视觉小说。<br><br>在一个遥远的宅邸里，深处寂静的森林中，四位来自不同种族的男人对你低语情话。<br><br>在他们中间，谁能赢得你心？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/ebfad025276460a98d7b4e541930c92f.webp?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/cc0ed77c3225acc7e7296d42cb62087d.poster.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/cc0ed77c3225acc7e7296d42cb62087d.webm?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/cc0ed77c3225acc7e7296d42cb62087d.mp4?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><table><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/52f89c29751958c07cf8f2d74bf53e4c.avif?t=1741358149\" width=74 height=74 /></span></td><td><strong>Shade</strong><br>表面上是自傲和傲慢的年轻贵族，然而内心深处，他是个单纯、幼稚的男孩。<br>他的魅力和自信显现在他的表情和每一个动作中。</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/f64edb9f09e44a915b344cee229a32eb.avif?t=1741358149\" width=74 height=74 /></span></td><td><strong>Al Feouz</strong><br>一个小巧、可爱的大眼男孩。<br>他那无尽的好奇心让他总是埋头于书本中，使他看起来天真且有些害羞。</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/929158f9f9e36f768c7f7bc372899f8c.avif?t=1741358149\" width=74 height=74 /></span></td><td><strong>Raul</strong><br>一只在森林深处长大的狼人。<br>他诚实直率，但在表达情感方面有些笨拙。</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/cb3fd67ea24cd16657f5cbff79bc9772.avif?t=1741358149\" width=74 height=74 /></span></td><td><strong>Tyrineon</strong><br>一位美丽的精灵，拥有温和友善的性格。<br>然而，在他那永远带着微笑的面容背后，隐藏着一张锋利无情的舌头。</td></tr></table><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/63133c61acb9fa5d56f31a0ac9b508f8.webp?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=50 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色专属路线</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/406e78fafa457fe13daecf9ef364bbac.poster.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/406e78fafa457fe13daecf9ef364bbac.webm?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/406e78fafa457fe13daecf9ef364bbac.mp4?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每个角色都有自己独特的故事路线。在序章之后，你将进入所选角色的路线，并跟随他们的个人故事直到最后。每个角色都是自己故事中的真正主角。<br>　<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于好感度的多重结局</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/8ceaf3614251c786333137a83a824f0c.poster.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/8ceaf3614251c786333137a83a824f0c.webm?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/8ceaf3614251c786333137a83a824f0c.mp4?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在 满月的宅邸 中没有 &quot;游戏结束&quot;。相反，每个选择都会影响角色的好感度。每个角色有三个结局，总共12个结局。你会发现怎样的结局？在你旅程的终点会等待着怎样的命运？<br>　<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸式动画视觉小说</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/f22da6324c210720d0a3328f240f01fd.poster.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/f22da6324c210720d0a3328f240f01fd.webm?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/f22da6324c210720d0a3328f240f01fd.mp4?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>流畅的动画带来身临其境的体验，使每个场景都充满活力与动感。享受游戏中的高质量动画CG，并尝试收集所有CG。<br>　<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/bac4c11457381dfb3da2f6055e0d4737.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><br>四位独特的男人在 满月的宅邸 等待着你。",
